<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>فَصْلٌ فِي جَزَاءِ الصَّيْدِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَهُوَ ضَرْبَانِ:</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١]</span> مَا لَهُ مِثْلٌ مِنَ النَّعَمِ، فَيَجِبُ فِيهِ ذَلِكَ المِثْلُ،<span style="color:#006d98"> وَهُوَ نَوْعَانِ:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span style="color:#006d98">أَحَدُهُمَا:</span> قَضَتْ فِيهِ الصَّحَابَةُ،<span style="color:#006d98"> وَمِنْهُ:</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> فِي النَّعَامَةِ:</span> بَدَنَةٌ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>- وَفِي حِمَارِ الوَحْشِ، وَبَقَرِهِ، وَإِيَّلٍ، وَتَيْتَلٍ،<span style="color:#006d98"> وَوَعِلٍ:</span> بَقَرَةٌ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَفِي الضَّبُعِ:</span> كَبْشٌ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>